On Monday Donald Trump gave a speech in front of 40,000 Boy Scouts at their annual Jamboree in West Virginia and it was... incredible.Rather than tone down his trademark political rhetoric whilst addressing a crowd consisting mostly of 7-10-year-olds, the President of the USA covered "fake news", his Electoral College victory and squeezed in digs at both Obama and Clinton.As a Scout leader, my stomach is in knots about what Trump did today. If you haven't watched it yet, don't. It's downright icky.This is like when an NBA player plays a 6-year-old and swats all of his shots. Trump's giving these boys the authentic Trump experience.Classy. Here's a rundown of some of the finer moments...